How to Explain to the Interviewer?

ğŸ”¹ "In our use case, we followed a mix of "Rehost", "Replatform", and "Retain" strategies because different components required different approaches."
ğŸ”¹ "We Rehosted large amounts of data from on-prem to AWS S3 without major changes."
